research_municipality_step.notes: Information gathered from multiple sources. There was a discrepancy regarding the Council Member for Place 2 and the Mayor Pro Tem. Sources [3] and [4] list Berry Phillips as Council Member Place 2 and Monte Sides as Mayor Pro Tem, while source [5] lists Sharlene T. Hetzel as both Place 2 and Mayor Pro-Tem. The information from sources [3] and [4] was prioritized due to consistency between them.
